data.description: Look no further, this is the home you've been looking for. It's located in Elkhorn school district.  It has a very cozy feel the moment you walk in the door. There is plenty of space with an open concept main level with newer vinyl flooring throughout. The living room is the perfect place to entertain. It has 9' ceiling, wood fireplace and a wet bar.  On the upstairs level there are 3 bedrooms, and the primary bedroom has its' own bathroom and private balcony. Fenced in yard with no back neighbors and is located in a quiet cul-de-sac. You are also close to shopping, and plenty of restaurants. Some other features are main floor laundry, fenced in backyard, patio was extended in 2019, and roof and gutters new 2019. Home sold as is.
